HEADWORD: Subterraneous
<hw>Sub`ter*ra"ne*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>subterraneus</ets>; <ets>sub</ets> under + <ets>terra</ets> earth.
