the earth; situated within the earth, or under ground; <as>as,
<ex>subterranean</ex> springs; a <ex>subterraneous</ex>
passage.</as></def> -- <wordforms><wf>Sub`ter*ra"ne*ous*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
